  "text": "To elucidate the mechanisms that govern early nucleolar large-subunit assembly, several laboratories, including ours (data not shown), have observed that cellular starvation extends the lifetime of a 27SB prerRNA-containing species [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Here, we have isolated these intermediates from starved yeast using tandem-affinity purification involving tagged ribosome assembly factors Nsa1 and Nop2 (Extended Data Fig. 1 ).",
